title: Dissecting the ‘All Stars 2’ Final With Janelle and Darrell | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
With all the rumors about the ‘All Stars 2’ final challenge flying around, Johnny brings on Janelle and Darrell to give a play-by-play of everything that went down, from the hectic puzzles on the first day to the drama surrounding the safes.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guests: Darrell Taylor and Janelle Casanave
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
Additional Production: Juliet Litman
